  <li>Work that fits with the rest of your life</li>
</ol>

<blockquote>
  <p>You don‚Äôt have to get all the ingredients of a fulfilling life from your job. It‚Äôs possible to find a job that pays the bills and excel in a side project; or to find a sense of meaning through philanthropy or volunteering; or to build great relationships outside of work.</p>
</blockquote>

